-- CK Life to Sell Some Ruinian Shares Privately, Raising Net HK$257 Million
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-09-29T15:05:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/ck-life-to-sell-some-ruinian-shares-privately-raising-net-hk-257-million.html
CK Life Sciences International 
(Holdings) Inc. will place 40 million shares in  Ruinian
International Ltd ., a 3.82 percent stake, raising a net HK$257
million, the company said in a Hong Kong stock exchange filing.  Morgan Stanley is the placing agent for the fully
underwritten sale, CK Life said today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  